{"type": "article", "id": 9903, "title": "隈研吾在台湾设计了一个木棚，还可以做演出", "description": "功能很多，还可以用作演出场所。", "date": "2015-05-22T13:35:34Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 893, "name": "隈研吾"}, {"id": 2776, "name": "台湾"}, {"id": 10513, "name": "拱形走廊"}], "category": 17, "author": 37534, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 50, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606160608hfBF9nEOMCHXJisU.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t近日，<a href=\"http://www.designboom.com/architecture/kengo-kuma-wind-eaves-pavilion-hsinchu-county-taiwan-05-21-2015/\" target=\"_blank\">designboom 网站的一则报道称</a>，日本设计师<a href=\"http://kkaa.co.jp\" target=\"_blank\">隈研吾和他的工作室</a>为台湾的一家小旅馆设计了一个多功能木结构走廊。这家小旅馆叫作<a href=\"http://nanyuan.theonestyle.com/english/index.asp\" target=\"_blank\">“南园人文客栈” </a>，位于台北市，距离桃园机场 40 分钟距离。走廊采取的是拱形结构，全木材料，使用了有限的金属元件，以追求自然感。拱形走廊上覆盖着 ETFE 膜。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606061606056w2s97o5fgLBWd1H.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t从内部望去，走廊的木质结构\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606160605RHLMNnZY1srU6XeP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"white-space:normal;\"> 木结构外覆盖着 ETFE 膜</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606160606v7nlhXQGiwqtTc4P.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t夜晚的灯光效果，走廊可以作为一个小型演出场所使用\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606160606u9DFyk3pYhei0vIU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t庞大的拱形\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606160607i3hla7pvTdq6CDH1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t另外一个角度看走廊\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606061606074dqQYjFJh1W2BpDV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t木质空间\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606160608RFWtZ8Q6j1N7g0vd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t从这张图你可以体会一下物和人的比例。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<em>题图来源：</em><a href=\"http://www.designboom.com/architecture/kengo-kuma-wind-eaves-pavilion-hsinchu-county-taiwan-05-21-2015/\" target=\"_blank\"><em>designboom</em></a> \r\n</p>\n\n\n"}